Welcome to Franconjugue!

This app helps you master French verb conjugations through interactive flashcards and a verb explorer.

  • Flashcards: Tap the card to reveal the answer, and tap again for the next card. Each card tests you on a random verb, tense, and pronoun.
  • Audio: Tap the verb or conjugation to hear it pronounced. Use the buttons for quick listening.
  • Verb Explorer: Browse all verbs and their full conjugation tables. Tap to jump to the current verb in the explorer.
  • Settings: Adjust which tenses and verb frequencies appear in flashcards. You can also enable or disable example phrases.
  • Progress: The app remembers your settings and history for a smooth learning experience.

Tip: For best results, use the app in full-screen mode on your device.

Created with for language learners.

French Verb Mnemonics & Tips

-ER Verbs Mnemonic

Mnemonic: e, es, e, ons, ez, ent

Rhyme: Je -e, Tu -es, Il -e... Nous -ons, Vous -ez, Ils -ent.

Example: parler je parle, tu parles, il parle, nous parlons...

-IR Verbs Mnemonic

Mnemonic: is, is, it, issons, issez, issent

Phrase: "IS, IS, IT ISSONS, ISSEZ, ISSENT"

Example: finir je finis, tu finis, il finit, nous finissons...

-RE Verbs Mnemonic

Mnemonic: s, s, , ons, ez, ent

Note: Il/Elle gets nothing theyre shy.

Example: vendre je vends, tu vends, il vend, nous vendons...

Boot Verbs (Stem-changing)

Mnemonic: Think of a boot shape covering forms: je, tu, il/elle, ils/elles

Rule: Stem changes apply inside the boot, but not to nous and vous.

Example: acheter jachte, tu achtes, nous achetons
